y:none;" src="http://gravatar.com/avatar/b41b40d04cc32e3e4f904f051c19deec" alt="" /> <img src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/Michele-Curnis-120x150.jpg" width="80" height="100" alt="Michele Curnis" class="avatar avatar-100 wp-user-avatar wp-user-avatar-100 alignnone photo" /></div><div id="author-description" class="padding-20"><meta itemprop="name" content="Michele Curnis"><meta itemprop="url" content=""><p></p><p class="add-author-info"> <a href="#"><i class="icon-facebook-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-twitter-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-google-plus-sign"></i></a></p> <a style="font-size: 11px;" href="http://www.gbopera.it/author/michele-curnis/">View all articles by Michele Curnis</a></div></div><div class="nav-block box-shadow-2px padding-20 clearfix"> <nav class="nav-single"><h3 class="assistive-text">Post navigation</h3> <span class="nav-previous"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/2013/02/un-ballo-in-maschera-di-verdi-primo-titolo-per-la-stagione-2013-del-bellini-di-catania/" rel="prev"><span class="meta-nav">&larr;</span> &#8220;Un ballo in maschera&#8221; di Verdi, primo titolo per la stagione 2013 del Bellini di Catania</a></span> <span class="nav-next"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/2013/02/il-nostro-e-amore-danime-andrea-chenier-al-teatro-regio-di-torino/" rel="next">Il nostro  amore danime! Andrea Chnier al Teatro Regio di Torino <span class="meta-nav">&rarr;</span></a></span> </nav><nav class="nav-single-hidden"> <span class="nav-previous"></span> <span class="nav-next"></span><div class="clear"></div> </nav></div><div class="comments-block box-shadow-2px clearfix"><div id="comments" class="comments-area"><div id="respond" class="comment-respond"><h3 id="reply-title" class="comment-reply-title">Lascia un commento <small><a rel="nofollow" id="cancel-comment-reply-link" href="/2013/02/dallanime-esultanti-sboccia-lamor-la-boheme-al-teatro-regio-di-torino/#respond" style="display:none;">Annulla risposta</a></small></h